select i_item_id
      ,i_item_desc 
      ,i_category 
      ,i_class 
      ,i_current_price
      ,sum(ss_ext_sales_price) as itemrevenue 
      ,sum(ss_ext_sales_price)*100/sum(sum(ss_ext_sales_price)) over
          (partition by i_class) as revenueratio
from	
	spark_catalog.qa_performance_database.store_sales
    	,item 
    	,date_dim
where 
	ss_item_sk = i_item_sk 
  	and i_category in ('Women', 'Electronics', 'Shoes')
  	and ss_sold_date_sk = d_date_sk
	and d_date between cast('2002-05-27' as date) 
                                and DATE_ADD(DATE '2002-05-27', 10)
group by 
	i_item_id
        ,i_item_desc 
        ,i_category
        ,i_class
        ,i_current_price
order by 
	i_category
        ,i_class
        ,i_item_id
        ,i_item_desc
        ,revenueratio

select  
   substr(w_warehouse_name,1,20)
  ,sm_type
  ,cc_name
  ,sum(case when (cs_ship_date_sk - cs_sold_date_sk <= 30 ) then 1 else 0 end)  as a_30_days
  ,sum(case when (cs_ship_date_sk - cs_sold_date_sk > 30) and 
                 (cs_ship_date_sk - cs_sold_date_sk <= 60) then 1 else 0 end )  as a_31_60_days
  ,sum(case when (cs_ship_date_sk - cs_sold_date_sk > 60) and 
                 (cs_ship_date_sk - cs_sold_date_sk <= 90) then 1 else 0 end)  as a_61_90_days
  ,sum(case when (cs_ship_date_sk - cs_sold_date_sk > 90) and
                 (cs_ship_date_sk - cs_sold_date_sk <= 120) then 1 else 0 end)  as a_91_120_days
  ,sum(case when (cs_ship_date_sk - cs_sold_date_sk  > 120) then 1 else 0 end)  as a_120_days_and_more
from
   catalog_sales
  ,warehouse
  ,ship_mode
  ,call_center
  ,date_dim
where
    d_month_seq between 1200 and 1200 + 11
and cs_ship_date_sk   = d_date_sk
and cs_warehouse_sk   = w_warehouse_sk
and cs_ship_mode_sk   = sm_ship_mode_sk
and cs_call_center_sk = cc_call_center_sk
group by
   substr(w_warehouse_name,1,20)
  ,sm_type
  ,cc_name
order by sm_type
        ,cc_name
limit 100
